song.title: Winterstorm
song.info:
Lyrics: As leader I remain aware as they all sleep I see my breath in the freezing air
Yet as I wander through the snow all alone Can't help but feel at home I wander
So silently I touch the ground that I traverse Move swift without a single sound
And as I wander through the snow, I'm strong alone Can't help but feel at home I wander
Predicting searching soulless eyes exit the dark Emerging now from night's disguise
And as I hunt throughout the night I walk alone Can't help but feel at home I'm where I belong
